# CODEOWNERS — the human PR review gate for the agentic harness.
#
# 🟩 NATIVE enforcement: when the repository ruleset requires CODEOWNERS review
# (set by demos/deploy/github/enforce-protections.ps1), GitHub itself BLOCKS merge
